title: Partition Table Doctor 3.5
description:
=== PROGRAM NOTES ===
Table Doctor will recover your data if the partition table,or boot sector on hard disk is lost or damaged. Partition may be lost or corrupted due to a virus attack, software failure, Fdisk or Partition Magic misapplication, and so on. Partition Table Doctor can recover partitions and get everything back.

Partition Table Doctor recovers from:
Hard drives (IDE / ATA / SATA / SCSI)
USB Hard Drives

=== installation instructions ===
1. Unpack & Install.
2. Enjoy! :)
